headline: Madison Mid Cap Fund Q4 2024 Investment Strategy Letter

headline: Expeditors Announces New President and Chief Executive Officer
summary: With the retirement announcement of Jeffrey S. Musser, EXPD's board of directors chooses Daniel R. Wall as the company's next president and chief executive officer.

headline: Expeditors: A Powerful Moat
summary: Expeditors boasts a robust moat, evidenced by achieving high ROE over decades while using no leverage. Read why I maintain my buy rating on EXPD stock.
